            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1715603366728-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1715603366728-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Combine your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> with your <strong>ground smoked paprika </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– these are your <strong>smokey breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Combine 20g <span class=\"text-purple\">[30g]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [40g] </span>of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>the <strong>softened butter</strong> with your <strong>BBQ sauce</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>BBQ butter</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1715603370574-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1715603370574-x400.jpg",
