      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped green chilli</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong> and <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> to the reserved bowl with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>green chilli dressing</strong></p>",
