    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> BBQ butter chicken </strong>with the <strong>green beans </strong>and<strong> sweet potato mash </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>green chilli dressing</strong> over the <strong>green beans </strong>and garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds </strong>– these are your <strong>chilli greens</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave the dressing and chilli rounds!</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
